{
  "id": "adv_bond_hrk_01_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "（次はどこの廃墟に行こうかしら）\n（一日で帰って来れない所は厳しいわよね……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Where should I go to next ruins）\n（It's hard to go to places that I can't take a day trip…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2500
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6240
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.333333299999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うわ。何、そのきったない建物",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow. What is‚ that ugly building",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～？　廃墟よ廃墟！\n次のオフにどこ行こうかなーって調べてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh~? Ruins‚ ruins!\nI was researching where to go next off day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "これとか、風情あるじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't there a nice vibe‚ here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ボロい洋館ね。それの何がいいのかしら\n見るからに怪しそうだし、汚いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an old Western-style building. What's so good about it?\nI can tell by just looking at it that it's suspicious and dirty",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "その古さがたまらないのよ\n傷一つにもロマンや歴史が詰まってて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't get enough of that oldness\nEven a single scar is filled with romance and history――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、最近、廃墟ブームの波がきてるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right right‚ recently‚ a wave of ruin boom is coming!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな暗い趣味にブームがくるのが謎なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a mystery how such a shady hobby became popular",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "暗い趣味は否定出来ない……で、でもこの旅館の廃墟は\n映画の撮影やコスプレイベントで使われたりしてて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't deny that it's a shady hobby… B-But‚ the ruins of this inn\nare used for filming movies and cosplay events!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "この前はDJイベントなんかもあったわ\nあとはそうね、謎解きイベントが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was also a DJ event recently\nOther than that‚ it's a puzzle-solving event――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "え、ちょっと待って。いろいろイベントが\n開催されてるみたいだけど、廃墟って集客出来るの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ wait a minute. It looks like there are various events\nbeing held‚ but can ruins attract visitors?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6333309174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "沢山人を呼べないからこそ、価値が上がってるのよ\nプラチナチケットなんて呼ばれてるくらいなんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it can't gather a lot of people‚ it's valuable\nAlso called the platinum ticket!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3333309174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。ここでライブの配信とかめずらしい企画を\n打てば、きっとお小遣い稼ぎくらいにはなるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. If I do live broadcasts and produce rare projects here‚\nI could definitely make some pocket money",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1333309174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、企画するにも規模感とか分からないし、やっぱり\n現地に行かないとよね……アレだけが気掛かりだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I don't know the scale of the event‚ and\nif I don't go there… that's the only ball and chain",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1999975841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "廃墟界隈、盛り上がってるのね。少し興味はあるけど\n………そ、その、出るんでしょ。アレが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ruins area‚ looks exciting. I'm a little interested\n…H-Hey‚ it's going to come out. That thing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9333293915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "アレって………？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That thing……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.733335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "お、お化けよ！\nこんないかにも～な建物に出ない訳がないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-Ghost!\nThere's no way~ it wouldn't appear in such a plausible building",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.633335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そんな頻繁に出ないわよ～\n実際私は見たことないし……出るって噂は聞くけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't come out that often~\nI've never actually seen it… but I've heard rumors that it's coming out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666688283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり出るんじゃない！\n廃墟でライブの企画は儲かると思ったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it‚ it's coming out!\nI thought planning a live show in the ruins would be profitable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.633335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "廃墟でライブ！？\nいいわね、楽しそう！　franさん天才だわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Live show in the ruins!?\nGreat‚ sounds fun! fran-san is a genius!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.933335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "企画書を作る前に、現地の下見をしに行きましょうよ！\n早速、次のオフの日はどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before creating a plan‚ let's go do some field research!\nImmediately‚ how about the next off day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3666759491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に話を進めないで！　絶対嫌。お化けが出るもの！\nうう……でも、お金を儲けるタイミングを逃すのも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't go ahead with the story on your own! Absolutely not. Ghosts appearing!\nUgh… but‚ missing opportunity to make money is also…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3000041962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、良かったらこれを機に、廃墟アイドルとして\nユニットを組まない？　新ジャンルの廃ドルよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ if you'd like‚ how about we use this as an opportunity\nto form a unit with ruin idols? A new genre of ruins-dol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9666708629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなマニアックなユニット、組まないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not going to form‚ such a maniacal unit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9000062307,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}